  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-01-03",
    "date": "2025-02-28T15:48:54Z",
    "text": "No Budget, No Pay Act \n\nThis bill withholds the salaries of Members of a chamber of Congress that has not agreed to a budget resolution for the next fiscal year\u00a0by April 15, as required by the Congressional Budget Act of 1974.\n\nSalaries are withheld from April 16 until the earlier of (1) the day on which the chamber of Congress agrees to a budget resolution for the next fiscal year, or (2) the last day of the Congress."
